leted at an age\nbetween 5 to 15 Myr. Dust depletion is very likely related to the build-up of\nlarger particles (ultimately rocks and planetesimals) and thus an indicator for\nthe onset of the period of planet formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 May 2000 23:01:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
