 the highest surface\nbrightness source in the galaxy at optical wavelengths, We discuss whether the\noutflow is powered by a low luminosity AGN or a compact nuclear starburst.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 May 2000 03:20:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Dec 2001 20:33:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
